@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Us";
}
<div class="container my-5">
    <!-- Row for text and image -->
    <div class="row align-items-center">
        <!-- Text Column -->
        <div class="col-md-8">
            <h1 class="h2 mb-3">About us</h1><br />
            <div class="overflow-auto" style="max-height: 500px;">
                <!-- Adjust max-height as needed -->
                <h3>About Aurora Brickwell</h3>
                <p>Welcome to Aurora's Brick Kingdom, where creativity meets construction! My name is Aurora Brickwell, and I'm thrilled to share my passion for LEGO® bricks with you.</p>
                <br />
                <h3>Our Story</h3>
                <p>Ever since I was a child, LEGO bricks have been an integral part of my life. From building towering castles to intricate spacecraft, the possibilities with LEGO bricks have always sparked my imagination. As I grew older, my love for LEGO only deepened, fueling my desire to share this joy with others.</p>
                <p>Driven by my passion and fueled by creativity, I embarked on a journey to create Aurora's Brick Kingdom—a place where LEGO enthusiasts of all ages can come together to explore, build, and inspire one another.</p>
                <br />
                <h3>What We Offer</h3>
                <p>At Aurora's Brick Kingdom, we offer a curated selection of LEGO sets, accessories, and merchandise to ignite your imagination and bring your creations to life. Whether you're a seasoned builder or just beginning your LEGO journey, we have something for everyone.</p>
                <br />
                <h3>Our Mission</h3>
                <p>Our mission is simple: to spread the joy of LEGO bricks far and wide. We believe that creativity knows no bounds and that every brick tells a story waiting to be told. Through our products, resources, and community, we aim to inspire creativity, foster imagination, and build lasting memories one brick at a time.</p>
                <br />
                <h3>Join Our Kingdom</h3>
                <p>Join us on this adventure as we build, create, and explore together. Whether you're looking for the perfect set to add to your collection or seeking inspiration for your next masterpiece, Aurora's Brick Kingdom is your destination for all things LEGO.</p>
                <p>Thank you for being a part of our journey. Together, let's build something extraordinary!</p>
                <p><strong>Happy bricking,<br>Aurora Brickwell</strong></p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Image Column -->
        <div class="col-md-4 text-center">
            <img src="/image.png" class="img-fluid mb-3" alt="Aurora Brickwell" style="max-width: 500px;"> <!-- Adjust the size as needed -->
        </div>
    </div>
</div>





